name: Galway Game Jam - Community Spirit
description:
A soon to be Witch delivery game!

Controls:

WASD - Move
Space - Jump
Space (While Jumping) - Fly
Double Tap Space (While Flying) - Dismount
Alt+F4 - Quit
Escape - Release Mouse

Programming by Shane O'Brien.
Art by Clare Byrne.

Witch 3d model and animations from the Asset Store
